# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>The Lyran Commonwealth's industrial wealth ensures its infantry are among the best-equipped in the Inner Sphere, fielding hardware that most armies reserve for elite formations as standard issue. LCAF field artillery platoons operate indirect-fire weapons that can engage targets well beyond line of sight, providing conventional infantry formations with area bombardment and fire-support capability. Crewed by troops armed with submachine guns and assault rifles for perimeter defense, these platoons are high-value assets that require dedicated security.</p>
</overview>

